<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>KarigarX AI — Custom Furniture Design</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r128/three.min.js"></script>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,700;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --cream:#FAF8F4;--cream2:#F2EDE4;--cream3:#E8E0D2;
  --bark:#3D2B1F;--bark2:#6B4C35;--bark3:#9E7355;
  --gold:#C9974A;--gold2:#E8B86D;
  --white:#FFFFFF;--black:#1A1008;
  --text:#2C1F0F;--text2:#6B5040;--text3:#A89080;
  --border:rgba(61,43,31,0.12);--border2:rgba(61,43,31,0.22);
  --shadow:rgba(61,43,31,0.15);--green:#4A6741;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--cream);color:var(--text);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px}::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--cream2)}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--bark3);border-radius:3px}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}
@keyframes float{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateY(-8px)}}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.5}}
@keyframes slideIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)}}
.nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;height:68px;background:rgba(250,248,244,0.95);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 32px;justify-content:space-between}
.nav-logo{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--bark);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.nav-logo span{color:var(--gold);font-style:italic}
.nav-logo-icon{width:34px;height:34px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--bark),var(--bark3));border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px}
.nav-actions{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:12px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:all 0.25s ease;outline:none}
.btn-primary{background:var(--bark);color:var(--cream);box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(61,43,31,0.3)}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--black);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.btn-secondary{background:transparent;color:var(--text2);border:1.5px solid var(--border2)}
.btn-secondary:hover{background:var(--cream2);border-color:var(--bark3)}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--text3);padding:10px 16px;font-size:13px}
.btn-ghost:hover{color:var(--text);background:var(--cream2)}
.btn-gold{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold2));color:var(--bark);font-weight:600;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(201,151,74,0.35)}
.btn-gold:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(201,151,74,0.4)}
.btn:disabled{opacity:0.4;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none!important}
.page{display:none;min-height:100vh;animation:fadeIn 0.4s ease}
.page.active{display:block}
#role-page{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh;padding:40px 24px;flex-direction:column}
.role-cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;max-width:640px;width:100%;margin-top:48px}
.role-card{background:var(--white);border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:24px;padding:40px 32px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s ease;text-align:center}
.role-card:hover{border-color:var(--gold);transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 20px 60px var(--shadow)}
.role-card h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--bark)}
.role-card p{color:var(--text3);font-size:14px}
.home-hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:120px 24px 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.home-hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 30%,rgba(201,151,74,0.08) 0%,transparent 70%)}
.section-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:16px}
.section-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px);font-weight:700;color:var(--bark);line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:12px}
.container{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 32px}
.section{padding:80px 0}
.cat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:16px;margin-top:16px}
.cat-card{background:var(--white);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:24px 16px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s ease;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.cat-card::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),var(--gold2));transform:scaleX(0);transition:transform 0.3s;transform-origin:left}
.cat-card:hover{border-color:var(--gold);transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(201,151,74,0.15)}
.cat-card:hover::after{transform:scaleX(1)}
.cat-card.selected{border-color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,151,74,0.06);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(201,151,74,0.2)}
.cat-icon{font-size:32px;margin-bottom:12px;display:block;transition:transform 0.3s}
.cat-card:hover .cat-icon{transform:scale(1.15) rotate(-5deg)}
.cat-name{font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:var(--bark);margin-bottom:4px}
.cat-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3)}
.chair-types-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:20px}
.chair-type-card{background:var(--white);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s ease}
.chair-type-card:hover{border-color:var(--gold);transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(201,151,74,0.15)}
.chair-type-card.selected{border-color:var(--gold);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(201,151,74,0.25)}
.chair-type-img{height:170px;background:var(--cream2);position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;overflow:hidden}
.chair-type-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.chair-type-badge{position:absolute;top:10px;left:10px;background:rgba(250,248,244,0.95);border-radius:20px;padding:4px 10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--bark)}
.chair-type-body{padding:16px}
.chair-type-name{font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--bark);margin-bottom:4px}
.chair-type-style{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3)}
.design-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:24px}
.design-card{background:var(--white);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s ease}
.design-card:hover{border-color:var(--gold);transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(201,151,74,0.18)}
.design-card.selected{border-color:var(--gold);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(201,151,74,0.3)}
.design-card-img{height:230px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.design-card-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;transition:transform 0.4s}
.design-card:hover .design-card-img img{transform:scale(1.06)}
.design-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(28,14,5,0.5) 0%,transparent 55%)}
.design-card-body{padding:18px}
.design-card-name{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:20px;color:var(--bark);margin-bottom:4px}
.design-badge{position:absolute;top:12px;right:12px;width:32px;height:32px;background:var(--gold);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;color:white;font-weight:700}
.config-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 360px;min-height:600px;gap:0;background:var(--white);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 8px 40px var(--shadow)}
.config-viewer{background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--cream) 0%,var(--cream2) 100%);position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-right:1px solid var(--border)}
.config-panel{overflow-y:auto;max-height:600px;padding:28px}
.config-section{margin-bottom:24px}
.config-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:12px}
.color-dot{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid transparent;transition:all 0.2s;flex-shrink:0}
.color-dot.sel{border-color:var(--bark)!important;transform:scale(1.2);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(201,151,74,0.35)}
.color-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}
.mpill{padding:7px 14px;border-radius:20px;border:1.5px solid var(--border2);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;background:transparent;color:var(--text2);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;outline:none}
.mpill:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--bark)}
.mpill.sel{border-color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,151,74,0.12);color:var(--bark);font-weight:600}
.pills-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}
.sw{margin-bottom:16px}
.sw label{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:6px}
.sw label span{color:var(--gold);font-weight:600}
input[type=range]{width:100%;height:4px;-webkit-appearance:none;border-radius:2px;background:var(--cream3);cursor:pointer;accent-color:var(--bark)}
.tog{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:12px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;margin-bottom:8px}
.tog.on{border-color:rgba(201,151,74,0.5);background:rgba(201,151,74,0.06)}
.tknob{width:36px;height:20px;background:var(--cream3);border-radius:10px;position:relative;transition:background 0.2s;flex-shrink:0}
.tknob.on{background:var(--bark)}
.tknob::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:3px;left:3px;width:14px;height:14px;background:white;border-radius:50%;transition:transform 0.2s;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)}
.tknob.on::after{transform:translateX(16px)}
.price-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--cream2),var(--cream));border:1.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;margin-top:20px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center}
.price-val{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:700;color:var(--bark)}
.viewer-hint{position:absolute;bottom:16px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:rgba(250,248,244,0.9);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:20px;padding:7px 16px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);white-space:nowrap}
.acc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}
.acc-item{border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;background:var(--cream2)}
.acc-item:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}
.acc-item.sel{border-color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,151,74,0.08)}
.upload-box{border:2px dashed var(--border2);border-radius:20px;padding:40px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s;background:var(--cream2);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.upload-box:hover{border-color:var(--gold)}
.upload-box input{position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:0;cursor:pointer;width:100%;height:100%}
.room-thumbs{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(100px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-top:12px}
.room-thumb{border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:4/3;position:relative;border:1.5px solid var(--border)}
.room-thumb img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;cursor:pointer}
.room-thumb-rm{position:absolute;top:4px;right:4px;width:20px;height:20px;background:rgba(28,14,5,0.7);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;font-size:11px;color:white}
.ai-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--bark),var(--bark2));border-radius:20px;padding:28px;color:white;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.ai-tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-radius:20px;padding:5px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:16px}
.ai-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:16px}
.ai-chip{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:20px;padding:6px 14px;font-size:13px}
.step-bar{position:fixed;top:68px;left:0;right:0;z-index:190;background:rgba(250,248,244,0.97);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:12px 32px;display:none;align-items:center;gap:0;overflow-x:auto}
.step-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex:1;min-width:fit-content}
.step-dot{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--border2);background:var(--cream2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text3);flex-shrink:0;transition:all 0.3s}
.step-dot.active{border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold);color:white}
.step-dot.done{border-color:var(--bark);background:var(--bark);color:white}
.step-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text3);white-space:nowrap}
.step-name.active{color:var(--bark);font-weight:600}
.step-line{flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border2);margin:0 8px;min-width:20px}
.step-line.done{background:var(--bark)}
.spinner{width:40px;height:40px;border:3px solid var(--cream3);border-top-color:var(--bark);border-radius:50%;animation:spin 0.8s linear infinite;margin:0 auto}
.vendor-stat{background:var(--white);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:28px;text-align:center}
.vendor-stat-num{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:40px;font-weight:700;color:var(--bark)}
.stats-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;margin:32px 0}
.product-item{background:var(--cream2);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.toast{position:fixed;bottom:28px;right:28px;z-index:999;background:var(--bark);color:white;border-radius:14px;padding:14px 24px;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(61,43,31,0.4);animation:slideIn 0.3s ease both;pointer-events:none}
.fopt{border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:10px 6px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text2);background:var(--cream2)}
.fopt.sel{border-color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,151,74,0.1);color:var(--bark)}
footer{background:var(--bark);color:rgba(250,248,244,0.7);padding:40px 32px;text-align:center;font-size:14px}
footer strong{color:var(--gold)}
@media(max-width:900px){.config-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr}.role-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}.stats-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
@media(max-width:768px){.nav{padding:0 16px}.container{padding:0 16px}.step-name{display:none}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav" id="main-nav" style="display:none">
  <div class="nav-logo" onclick="goHome()">
    <div class="nav-logo-icon">🪑</div>
    Karigar<span>X</span> AI
  </div>
  <div class="nav-actions">
    <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="goHome()">Home</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="startDesign()">Start Designing</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="step-bar" id="step-bar">
  <div class="step-item"><div class="step-dot" id="sd1">1</div><span class="step-name" id="sn1">Category</span></div>
  <div class="step-line" id="sl1"></div>
  <div class="step-item"><div class="step-dot" id="sd2">2</div><span class="step-name" id="sn2">Chair Type</span></div>
  <div class="step-line" id="sl2"></div>
  <div class="step-item"><div class="step-dot" id="sd3">3</div><span class="step-name" id="sn3">Design</span></div>
  <div class="step-line" id="sl3"></div>
  <div class="step-item"><div class="step-dot" id="sd4">4</div><span class="step-name" id="sn4">Configurator</span></div>
  <div class="step-line" id="sl4"></div>
  <div class="step-item"><div class="step-dot" id="sd5">5</div><span class="step-name" id="sn5">Room</span></div>
  <div class="step-line" id="sl5"></div>
  <div class="step-item"><div class="step-dot" id="sd6">6</div><span class="step-name" id="sn6">AI Report</span></div>
</div>

<!-- ROLE PAGE -->
<div id="role-page" class="page active">
  <div class="section-label" style="animation:fadeUp 0.6s ease both">Welcome to the future of furniture</div>
  <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,60px);font-weight:700;color:var(--bark);line-height:1.1;text-align:center;animation:fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;animation-fill-mode:both">Design your world,<br/><em style="color:var(--gold)">your way.</em></div>
  <p style="color:var(--text3);font-size:15px;margin-top:16px;text-align:center;max-width:400px;animation:fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both;animation-fill-mode:both">KarigarX AI brings artisanal craft and cutting-edge intelligence together. Who are you?</p>
  <div class="role-cards" style="animation:fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;animation-fill-mode:both">
    <div class="role-card" onclick="goUser()"><span style="font-size:48px;display:block;margin-bottom:20px">👤</span><h3>I'm a User</h3><p>Browse, customize & order bespoke furniture crafted to your vision</p></div>
    <div class="role-card" onclick="goVendor()"><span style="font-size:48px;display:block;margin-bottom:20px">🏭</span><h3>I'm a Vendor</h3><p>List your designs, manage pricing & materials, grow your workshop</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- HOME PAGE -->
<div id="home-page" class="page">
  <div class="home-hero">
    <div class="home-hero-bg"></div>
    <div style="animation:float 5s ease-in-out infinite;font-size:80px;margin-bottom:24px">🪑</div>
    <p class="section-label">✦ AI-Powered Custom Furniture</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(40px,6vw,80px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.05;color:var(--bark);margin-bottom:20px">Design furniture that<br/>feels like <em style="color:var(--gold)">you.</em></h1>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:var(--text2);max-width:480px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:48px">From a single chair to an entire home — design, customize, and order precision-crafted furniture powered by AI.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size:16px;padding:14px 32px" onclick="startDesign()">Start Designing ✦</button>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="document.getElementById('cat-section').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Browse Categories ↓</button>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:48px;margin-top:60px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center">
      <div style="text-align:center"><div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:var(--bark)">3,200+</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:4px">Designs Created</div></div>
      <div style="text-align:center"><div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:var(--bark)">98%</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:4px">Satisfaction</div></div>
      <div style="text-align:center"><div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:var(--bark)">15+</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:4px">Categories</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="cat-section" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">✦ 12 Categories</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">What would you like<br/>to design?</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--text2);font-size:15px;margin-bottom:40px">From statement chairs to full bedroom suites — choose your canvas.</p>
      <div class="cat-grid" id="home-cat-grid"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section" style="background:var(--cream2);border-top:1px solid var(--border)">
